WEBVTT

00:01:59.768 --> 00:02:02.037
Fulani herdsmen crisis

00:02:02.061 --> 00:02:03.808
and Boko Haram,

00:02:04.768 --> 00:02:06.169
I ask you:

00:02:06.193 --> 00:02:09.453
What will four times that number do?

00:02:11.614 --> 00:02:14.955
To do my part to solve this challenge,

00:02:14.979 --> 00:02:19.301
in 2012, I moved to a small village
in northern Nigeria,

00:02:20.507 --> 00:02:24.994
in the center of the area
most recently hit

00:02:25.018 --> 00:02:31.696
by the spread of insecurity,
brutal bombings and searing poverty,